## 5. Layer Responsibility Breakdown

| Layer | Responsibility | Key Modules |
|-------|---------------|-------------|
| **Presentation** | Render UI, capture user input (audio, text), display results, animate transitions | React pages, components, Framer Motion, TalkingHead canvas |
| **State** | Global app state, session management, pipeline progress tracking, chat history | Zustand `appStore.js` вҖ” single flat store with slices |
| **Service** | Business logic, API orchestration, data transformation, pipeline coordination | `gemini.js`, `elevenlabs.js`, `avatar.js`, `rag.js`, `storyPipeline.js`, `firebase.js` |
| **API / External** | Raw network calls, authentication, data persistence, file storage | Gemini API, ElevenLabs WebSocket, Firebase Firestore/Storage/Functions |

---

## 6. Tech Stack (Locked)

| Layer | Technology | Version | Justification |
|-------|-----------|---------|---------------|
| **Runtime** | Node.js | 20 LTS | Stable, Vite-compatible |
| **Frontend** | React | 18.x | Component model, ecosystem, hooks |
| **Build** | Vite | 6.x | Sub-second HMR, zero-config React |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS | 4.x | Utility-first, rapid iteration via `@tailwindcss/vite` |
| **Routing** | React Router | 6.x | Declarative client-side SPA routing |
| **State** | Zustand | 5.x | Zero boilerplate, no providers needed |
| **Animation** | Framer Motion | 12.x | Declarative page transitions, micro-interactions |
| **3D Avatar** | TalkingHead.js | latest | Purpose-built talking avatar with ElevenLabs lip-sync |
| **Avatar Model** | Ready Player Me (GLB) | вҖ” | Custom avatar with ARKit + Oculus viseme morph targets |
| **Avatar Anims** | Mixamo (FBX) | вҖ” | Free idle/talking/gesture animations |
| **Core LLM** | Gemini 2.0 Flash | latest | Multimodal audio+text+image, fast, generous free tier |
| **Embeddings** | Gemini Embedding API | latest | Vector embeddings for RAG pipeline |
| **Image Gen** | Imagen 3 (via Gemini) | latest | Story illustration generation |
| **TTS** | ElevenLabs WebSocket API | v1 | Natural voice, native TalkingHead lip-sync integration |
| **Database** | Cloud Firestore | v10 | Real-time sync, offline cache, native vector search |
| **File Storage** | Firebase Storage | v10 | Audio recordings, AI images, e-books, cached TTS |
| **Server Logic** | Cloud Functions (Firebase) | v2 | RAG orchestration, heavy AI processing |
| **Auth** | None | вҖ” | Anonymous Zustand session IDs for demo |

