## 9. Data Model (Firestore Collections)

### Collection: `stories`

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| `id` | string (auto) | Document ID |
| `title` | string | Auto-generated or user-provided title |
| `originalAudioUrl` | string | Firebase Storage URL for raw recording |
| `transcription` | string | Original language text |
| `language` | string | e.g. "semai", "temiar", "jakun" |
| `tribe` | string | Cultural group identifier |
| `elderName` | string | Optional narrator name |
| `scenes` | array | Scene objects (see below) |
| `createdAt` | timestamp | Creation time |
| `tags` | string[] | Searchable tags |

**Scene sub-document:**

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| `originalText` | string | Text in indigenous language |
| `translationEn` | string | English translation |
| `translationMs` | string | Malay translation |
| `imageUrl` | string | Firebase Storage URL for illustration |
| `audioUrl` | string | Cached ElevenLabs narration URL |
| `culturalNote` | string | Gemini-generated cultural annotation |

---

### Collection: `knowledge_base`

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| `id` | string (auto) | Document ID |
| `content` | string | Cultural knowledge text |
| `category` | string | `"folklore"` / `"medicine"` / `"history"` / `"skills"` / `"traditions"` / `"kinship"` |
| `language` | string | e.g. "semai" |
| `tribe` | string | Cultural group |
| `embedding` | vector(768) | Gemini embedding for vector search |
| `source` | string | Attribution / source reference |
| `tags` | string[] | Searchable tags |

---

### Collection: `vocabulary`

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| `id` | string (auto) | Document ID |
| `word` | string | Indigenous word |
| `language` | string | Language identifier |
| `pronunciationUrl` | string | Audio reference URL |
| `meaningEn` | string | English meaning |
| `meaningMs` | string | Malay meaning |
| `usageExample` | string | Example sentence |
| `culturalContext` | string | Usage context / nuance |
| `category` | string | Word category |

