## 12. UI/UX Design Direction

### Color Palette

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `--bg-deep` | `#0a0e17` | Page backgrounds |
| `--bg-surface` | `#111827` | Card / panel backgrounds |
| `--bg-elevated` | `#1f2937` | Hover states, modals |
| `--accent` | `#00e5a0` | Primary CTA, highlights, active states |
| `--accent-dim` | `#00b37d` | Secondary accent, borders |
| `--text-primary` | `#f1f5f9` | Main text |
| `--text-secondary` | `#94a3b8` | Muted text, labels |
| `--danger` | `#ef4444` | Errors, recording indicator |
| `--vocab-bg` | `#00e5a01a` | Vocabulary highlight background |
| `--vocab-border` | `#00e5a066` | Vocabulary highlight border |

### Typography

| Use | Font | Fallback |
|-----|------|----------|
| Headings | `'Outfit', sans-serif` | System sans-serif |
| Body | `'Inter', sans-serif` | System sans-serif |
| Mono / data | `'JetBrains Mono', monospace` | System monospace |

### Page-Level UI Wireframes

#### Home Page
- **Hero section**: Full-viewport, animated particle/pattern background evoking forest canopy. Tagline "Echoing Ancestral Voices into the Digital Future" with glowing emerald accent animation. CTA buttons to StoryWeaver and Digital Elder.
- **Feature cards**: 3 cards (StoryWeaver, Digital Elder, Pronunciation Lab) with icons, descriptions, and hover scale/glow effects. Use Framer Motion stagger animation on scroll.
- **Stats/impact bar**: "500+ languages at risk В· 1 platform to preserve them"
- **Footer**: Minimal вҖ” Borneo HackWKND 26 credit, team names.

#### StoryWeaver Page
- **Left panel (40%)**: Audio recorder with pulsing waveform visualization (Web Audio API AnalyserNode). Large record/stop button with red pulse animation during recording. Timer showing recording duration.
- **Center**: Pipeline progress вҖ” vertical stepper showing stages (transcribing вҶ’ translating вҶ’ illustrating вҶ’ narrating вҶ’ complete) with animated progress indicators and checkmarks.
- **Right panel (60%)**: E-Book viewer that builds in real-time as pipeline completes. Bilingual layout: left column = original language text, right column = English/Malay translation. Full-width illustration between text blocks. Audio player per scene. Page navigation.
- **Bottom drawer**: Story archive вҖ” grid of previously saved story cards.

#### Digital Elder Page
- **Left panel (40%)**: 3D avatar canvas (TalkingHead). Full-height, dark background. Avatar should be prominent вҖ” this is the wow factor.
- **Right panel (60%)**: Chat interface. Dark chat bubbles for elder responses, lighter for user. Indigenous vocabulary terms highlighted with emerald accent underline + tooltip on hover. Knowledge panel below chat showing retrieved source documents.
- **Chat input**: Full-width text input with send button. Optional: microphone button for voice input.

#### Pronunciation Lab Page
- **Center layout**: Avatar on top, phrase card in middle, pronunciation meter below.
- **Phrase card**: Indigenous phrase in large text, romanized pronunciation guide, English/Malay meaning. "Listen" button (avatar speaks it), "Try it" button (user records).
- **Pronunciation meter**: Animated circular gauge showing accuracy %. Color-coded (red вҶ’ yellow вҶ’ green).
- **Progress tracker**: Sidebar showing streak,  words mastered, accuracy trend.

