## 14. Demo Script (3 minutes)

| Timestamp | Beat | Script |
|-----------|------|--------|
| **0:00вҖ“0:25** | **Hook** | "Every two weeks, an indigenous language dies forever. Southeast Asia is home to over 500 languages at risk. We built EchoRoots to fight back вҖ” using AI to preserve voices before they're lost." |
| **0:25вҖ“0:45** | **Meet the Elder** | Navigate to Digital Elder page. 3D avatar loads вҖ” blinks, breathes, shifts weight. "Meet our Digital Elder вҖ” an AI guardian powered by real indigenous knowledge." |
| **0:45вҖ“1:30** | **StoryWeaver Live** | Switch to StoryWeaver. Team member speaks a pre-prepared 30-second folktale. Show real-time pipeline: transcription вҶ’ translation вҶ’ AI illustrations appearing вҶ’ bilingual e-book assembled. **This is the money shot.** |
| **1:30вҖ“2:15** | **Digital Elder Q&A** | Return to Digital Elder. Type: "What plant treats headaches in Semai tradition?" Avatar lip-syncs the answer. Vocabulary highlights appear. "Every answer is grounded in verified indigenous knowledge вҖ” not hallucinated." |
| **2:15вҖ“2:45** | **Pronunciation Lab** | Quick demo: avatar speaks a Semai phrase. User attempts it. Score: 82%. Tips shown. "Making language learning interactive and fun." |
| **2:45вҖ“3:00** | **Close** | "Every elder who passes takes a library with them. EchoRoots ensures their voice echoes forever." Show growing story archive. |

