## 15. Risk Matrix & Mitigation

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-------------|--------|------------|
| Avatar GLB fails to load | Low | High | Pre-record a video of avatar working. Show video + explain pipeline. |
| ElevenLabs quota or latency | Medium | Medium | Fall back to browser `SpeechSynthesis` API. Less impressive but functional. |
| Imagen 3 slow (>10s/image) | Medium | Medium | Pre-cache one complete StoryWeaver run. Show cached result + explain live pipeline. |
| Venue WiFi dies | Medium | Critical | Pre-load everything in Firestore offline cache. Use cached demo experience. |
| Pronunciation eval unreliable | High | Low | Skip feature entirely. StoryWeaver + Digital Elder is already winning. |
| Gemini API rate limit | Low | High | Request queuing + exponential backoff + cache all demo responses in localStorage. |
| TalkingHead lib issues | Low | High | Static avatar image + ElevenLabs audio playing separately. |
| Firestore vector search inaccuracy | Medium | Medium | Tune vector similarity threshold. Fall back to keyword search. |
| Browser MediaRecorder incompatibility | Low | Medium | Test on Chrome/Edge. Provide pre-recorded audio fallback. |

